## Copy voice

See `~/.claude/skills/ui-ios/copy-voice.md`. No lorem ipsum, no "Lightning fast / Powered by AI" filler. Cancel left, primary right. Capitalize "Done", "Cancel", "Save". If real copy is missing, STOP and ask the user.

## Adding new tokens

If you need a value that doesn't exist in `Theme.*`: STOP. Ask the user to extend the token set. NEVER add magic numbers inline.

## Hard HIG rules (non-negotiable)

1. Touch targets ≥ 44pt.
2. Dynamic Type supported on every text element.
3. Safe area respected (no `.ignoresSafeArea` without a documented `// SAFE-AREA-IGNORE:` reason).
4. Swipe-back gesture preserved on every `NavigationStack` push.
5. VoiceOver labels on every icon-only `Button`.
6. SF Symbols for system icons.
7. `.sheet` / `.fullScreenCover` / `.alert` / `.confirmationDialog` used per their HIG roles.
